<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<title>Help</title>
	<base target="_top">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./css/style.css"/>
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
	<script type="text/javascript" src="./js/thankssaurik.js"></script>
</head>

<body class="pinstripe">
    <panel>
        <label>All Themes</label>
            <fieldset>
                <div>
                    <p>Try reinstalling the theme and Winterboard/ Anemone</p>
                    <p>Check for updates</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p>Anemone:</p>
                    <p>Use with "WB Patch" disabled</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p>Winterboard:</p>
                    <p>Enable "WB Patch" above all other themes (assuming the theme includes one)</p>
                    <p>Install <a href="https://cydia//package/com.bensge.customclockicon" target="_new">Custom Clock Icon</a> or <a href="https://cydia//package/org.coolstar.customclock" target="_new">CustomClock</a> for the clock hands to be themed</p>
                    <p>Install IconBundles</p>
                </div>
            </fieldset>

        <label>Glyphs/cjGlyphs</label>
            <fieldset>
                <div>
                    <p>General:</p>
                    <p>Enable both cjGlyphs and Glyphs</p>
                    <p>Put cjGlyphs above Glyphs</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p>Black Version:</p>
                    <p>Use instead of normal base theme.</p>
                </div>
            </fieldset>

        <label>Activator Icon</label>
            <fieldset>
                <div>
                    <p>Follow <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/iOSthemes/comments/2rdwdp/me1_activator_icon0_how_to_theme_the_stubborn/?" target="_new">this tutorial</a> for Activator to be themed.</p>
                </div>
            </fieldset>
        
        <label>If All Else Fails</label>
            <fieldset>
                <div>
                    <p><a href="https://cj81499.github.io/depictions/contact.html" target="_new">Contact Me</a></p>
                </div>
            </fieldset>
    </panel>
</body>
</html>
